freesynergy-default-description =
    The official FreeSynergy icon set — a clean, modern SVG icon library.

    Contains icons for all system actions, application launchers, file types (MIME types),
    status indicators, devices, and places. All icons are scalable SVGs that adapt their
    stroke color to the active desktop theme, ensuring consistent appearance across
    Midnight Blue, Nordic Dark, Cloud White, and custom themes.

freesynergy-default-features =
    - Scalable SVG icons — crisp at any resolution
    - Adapts stroke color to the active theme
    - Covers apps, actions, status, MIME types, devices, and places
    - Designed in a clean modern line style
    - Compatible with custom and community themes
